# - Memory peak: 2.1GB
# - CPU usage: 25% (single core)
# 
# With Matter optimizations:
# - Processing time: 2.3s (4.6x faster!)
# - Memory peak: 450MB (4.7x less!)
# - CPU usage: 85% (all cores)
# - Profiling overhead: <1%
# - Leak detection overhead: <2%
